    "attributes": {
        "action": "Provide a minimum of 100 litres of clean water per person daily, free of charge",
        "additional_details": "Water is now an expensive commodity.\r\nThere is no option of choice of supplier in the water supply industry for private households.\r\nWater is a life essential and any modern country should be required to provide a minimum amount free of charge to maintain health in the population.",
        "background": "Water supply is fast becoming one of the most expensive utilities.\r\nI believe every UK citizen should be entitled to a minimum amount, supplied free of charge by all regional water companies, enough to provide the basic human needs and maintain health and hygiene at a good standard.",
